data.description: WELCOME HOME!!! 4 BEDROOM, 3 FULL BATH HOME LOCATED ON A CORNER LOT - .83 ACRES - IN DESIRABLE SOUTHEAST BULLOCH SCHOOL DISTRICT.  HARDY PLANK SIDING AND BRICK ENCOMPASS THE EXTERIOR AND THE LARGE BACKYARD IS COMPLETELY FENCED-IN WITH PRIVACY FENCING.  THE FOYER OPENS TO AN OPEN FLOOR PLAN, COMPLETE WITH A FORMAL DINING ROOM, SPACIOUS KITCHEN WITH GRANITE, CUSTOM CABINETRY AND STAINLESS STEEL APPLICANCES, A BREAKFAST NOOK AND A LARGE LIVING ROOM WITH GORGEOUS NEW BUILT-INS.    THE MASTER IS OFFERED AS A SPLIT FLOOR PLAN AND BOASTS A TREY CEILING, DOUBLE VANITIES, SEPARATE TILED SHOWER AND SOAKING TUB IN MASTER BATH. 3 ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS AND 2 ADDITIONAL BATHROOMS ARE ALL COMPLETE WITH CUSTOM TRIMMED ACCENT WALLS TO SET THEM APART FROM EACH OTHER. BOARD AND BATTING HAS BEEN ADDED TO THE FOYER, DINING AND HALL AREA AS WELL. LUXURY VINYLE PLANK FLOORING ABOUNDS THROUGHOUT ALL COMMON AREAS. IN-GROUND IRRIGATION, COVERED PATIO, AND CUSTOM PAINT/FIXTURES ARE ADDED BONUSES TO COMPLETE THIS
